Pat Conaty:

" Munibnb. Basically this would be an alliance of local authorities working in partnership with local residents who want to let out rooms. Munibnb would like Airbnb fund the allied update of the apps and platform to promote fair and local trade that would also ensure hotel taxes are paid and lettings are ethical. In South Korea the Munibnb concept is being developed by Seoul and other cities."


